  "info": {
    "name": "TexaPay Mobile API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "Session-cookie based Mobile API for TexaPay. Set baseUrl environment variable to your ngrok or local URL.\n\n=== TRANSFER TESTING INSTRUCTIONS ===\n\n1. Get a Quote:\n   - Use the \"Transfers - Quote\" request\n   - Save the `quote.id` and `quote.ref` from the response\n\n2. Set Variables:\n   - Update `quoteId` with the ID from the quote response\n   - Update `quoteRef` with the reference from the quote response\n\n3. Confirm Transfer:\n   - Use the \"Transfers - Confirm\" request\n   - It will automatically use all required fields from environment variables\n\n4. Check Status & Payout:\n   - Use \"Transfers - Payin Status\" to poll the pay-in\n   - Then use \"Transfers - Payout\" and \"Transfers - Payout Status\" as needed\n\n5. Receipts:\n   - Use \"Transfers - Receipt URL\" (HTML shared link)\n   - Use \"Transfers - Receipt PDF\" to get a signed PDF URL\n   - Use \"Transfers - Share URL\" to generate a public signed link\n\nNote: Make sure to log in first to establish a session."
  },
